item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】PACK - SPONGEBOB | DISCOGRAPHY [ALAC] + Bonus/Unreleased (13 albums)
item.description:
SpongeBob’s entire discography has arrived to ShareMania

only missing album: The Musical: The Sponge Who Could Fly
only missing songs: “Squidward’s Clarinet” & “Cha Ching” (bonus tracks from an enhanced edition of “The Yellow Album” /// and “Team Work” & “Thank Gosh it’s Monday” (from the film Sponge Out of Water)

The rest of the discography it’s all complete!
I’ll make another post with the international versions of the SpongeBob’s albums, this is only in english

THE FOLDER CONTAINS:
(2001) ORIGINAL THEME HIGHLIGHTS
(2004) [UNRELEASED] [MP3] THE SPONGEBOB MOVIE SCORE
(2004) [FLAC] THE SPONGEBOB MOVIE SOUNDTRACK
(2005) THE YELLOW ALBUM
(2006) THE BEST DAY EVER
(2009) GREATEST HITS (DELUXE + BONUS TRACK)
(2012) IT’S A SPONGEBOB CHRISTMAS!
(2015) SPONGE OUT OF WATER MOVIE SCORE
(2015) SPONGE OUT OF WATER MOVIE SOUNDTRACK
(2017) THE NEW MUSICAL
(2021) SPONGE ON THE RUN MOVIE SCORE
(2021) SPONGE ON THE RUN MOVIE SOUNDTRACK
(2023) KAMP KORAL SOUNDTRACK

Employee of the Month (Spongebob’s Movie OST bonus track)
The Very First Christmas
The Patrick Star Show Theme
